OL,6,G                                Vo%    
OL,7,BLee Brennan is, in his own      W(0`,# 
OL,8,Bwords, "absolutely exhausted". The boys
OL,9,BfromE911Bare in the middle of their UK 
OL,10,Btour, and Lee's worried he mayElose his
OL,11,EvoiceBat any minute!Q                  
OL,13,B"This is the first time we've done live
OL,14,Bgigs," Lee tells Club.E"My throatBhas  
OL,15,Bbeen taking aEhammeringBbut I've been  
OL,16,Bdrinking honey and lemon!"             
OL,18,B"I am shattered after our gigs but the 
OL,19,Badrenalin meansEI can't sleep till 3am"
