OL,5,EON TOUR WITH 911!               V|4    
OL,6,G                                Vo%    
OL,7,B911's Lee describes the responseW(0`,# 
OL,8,Bthe boys have had to their tour so far 
OL,9,BasE"mental".                           
OL,10,B                                       
OL,11,B"When we were inELiverpool,BaboutE300  
OL,12,Bfans were swarming around the hotel and
OL,13,Bit was quite mad. Some of them had even
OL,14,Ebooked roomsBand were staying there!"  
OL,16,BDo they get up to anyErawk and roll    
OL,17,Etomfoolery?B"Spike sometimes stays up  
OL,18,Buntil 6am but we're all knuckling down 
OL,19,Bto the work and need rest," admits Lee.
