OL,5,EON TOUR WITH 911!               V|4    
OL,6,G                                Vo%    
OL,7,BLee Brennan's been whiling away W(0`,# 
OL,8,Bhis time on the 911 tour bus listening 
OL,9,Bto the aptly-namedEOpen RoadBalbum!    
OL,10,B                                       
OL,11,B"I sit on the top deck of the bus and  
OL,12,Blisten toEGary BarlowBon my personal   
OL,13,Bstereo. Actually, I don't think he     
OL,14,Breleased what he wanted to. Record     
OL,15,Bcompanies have a lot of say in what's  
OL,16,Bput on an artist's album," says Lee.   
OL,18,B"We get four days off after the tour   
OL,19,Bso I'llEtake a short break in Carlisle"
