OL,5,EON TOUR WITH 911!               V|4    
OL,6,G                                Vo%    
OL,7,BLee from 911 says their next    W(0`,# 
OL,8,Bsingle,EParty People,Bisn't an accurate
OL,9,Breflection of the band's lifestyle.    
OL,11,B"I'm still quite shy when I'm out with 
OL,12,Bmy mates. If I go too mad, people think
OL,13,BI must be acting like anEarrogant pop  
OL,14,Estar.BI shouldn't care but I do," says 
OL,15,Bthe pint-sized popster.                
OL,17,B"The best party I ever went to was when
OL,18,BI was 16. I got drunk and ended up     
OL,19,Edancing with a blow-up doll!"Bhe laughs
