OL,8,Elisten to tapes andEanalyseBwhether    
OL,9,Bthey were any good live! "I don'tBlike 
OL,10,Blistening to my ownBvoice," saysBLee.  
OL,12,B"We had to rehearseBwith theBband for a
OL,13,Bfortnight before the tour and learn to 
OL,14,EbreatheBin a way that would allow us to
OL,15,Bdo theEdance routinesBas well.         
OL,17,B"It sounds silly but it's actually     
OL,18,BquiteEhard to remember how to breathe!"
OL,19,Bremarks Lee.                           
